{"tid":1736661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【守護孩子並沒有與曾鈺成就撤離理大安排達成共識，並代表年青人接受安排】","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:29:58.000Z","uid":231896,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e098b07138753821c15283e6ecc20fc882f64a0","tid":1736661,"uid":231896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:50:34.000Z","msg":"今晚曾鈺成指提供車輛予現場人士撤出，情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.過程中，守孩成員並沒有代表年青人與年青人傾，遵守沒有大台為原則，我們只向曾生作初步了解。<br />\n<br />\n2.我們只清楚表達安排必須乎合相關條件：年青人必須不被捕，不用通過警方審問，自由地離開。但因為星期日警方並沒予足夠時間讓年青人離開，更在他們離開時作逮捕，嚴重違反承諾及誠信。在此背景下，我們並不相信警方在所有人離開時，不作拘捕，甚至虐打。<br />\n<br />\n3.曾先生表示並不會讓步，我們並不同意，更未作出任何同意及協定。<br />\n<br />\n4.守孩原則是尊重自決。部份年青人接受此安排，我們清楚陳明被捕風險，但仍尊重他們選擇跟車。<br />\n<br />\n5.更由於守孩不同意曾先生安排，守孩成員不會坐上此車。<br />\n<br />\n6.因此，有指「跟守孩上車等如自首」，希望讓大家知我們並沒有帶或邀請他們跟車，更不認同無犯法者需要自首。年青人接受跟車的安排，均由他們自己辦理及申請，並沒有經守孩之手。<br />\n<br />\n7. 有部分守孩成員因著各種自身理由，如身體狀況、家人擔憂、需要服用藥物等，接受理大校方安排離開。仍有部分守孩留守理大與手足共同進退。<br />\n<br />\n希望讓大家更能了解，更明白為何我們堅持必需「放人」，其實問題關鍵是警方的欺騙及失信！請各位集中火力，逼使政府回應訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2151802395114124?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1561265357501167%2Fposts%2F2151802395114124%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=12d86f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1561265357501167/posts/2151802395114124?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"724c3da7a4e2507ccd77eb7e45dbc525e7487aae","tid":1736661,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2ca1d593ac558a74e2c83212876bd30e65b2c8","tid":1736661,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"正視聽 手足 不是自首 不是投降<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1736630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1736630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f37212429f0b9ddf9242c710ec7ee50a44fd9f14","tid":1736661,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"守護孩子嘅爸爸媽媽 好多謝您哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fd89aed2754de15b3e93e5c87ab07ea5598e07","tid":1736661,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:30:36.000Z","msg":"守護孩子心水清"},{"pid":"d28b558975f56964ed7fd82ab624243ef952b32c","tid":1736661,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:46:08.000Z","msg":"守護孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9f7791b7f2ef18a0fe2bc29511dda9f8d6f061","tid":1736661,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"咪住 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地有份搭路救朱媛？"},{"pid":"34cceac6a67c1450770887c1b80e0f40134ed568","tid":1736661,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}